summary: As more tech companies accelerate into investing in artificial intelligence and their own AI infrastructure, Moor Insights & Strategy founder, CEO, and chief analyst Patrick Moorhead and Futurum CEO Daniel Newman debate the companies that are positioned to be the biggest laggards in AI space.
